        <updateDate>2011-07-21T20:16:15Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Firearm Recidivist Sentencing Act of 2011 - Amends the federal criminal code to provide that individuals are subject to the 25-year mandatory minimum prison term for carrying or using a firearm while committing a violent crime or drug trafficking offense only if they have been previously convicted of such offense and such conviction has become final. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
